import MirrorLink from "../containers/MirrorLink"
import Banner from "./Banner"

const TerraBanner = () => (
  <Banner title="Need something faster?" dismiss>
    Use <MirrorLink /> for 10x speed and lower transaction fee!
  </Banner>
)

export default TerraBanner
